title: Obamas in talks to create shows with Netflix: NYT
text:
Obamas in talks to create shows with Netflix: NYT Friday, March 09, 2018 - 01:11 
According to the New York Times, the former U.S. president is in advanced talks with Netflix to produce a series of high-profile shows.
